= JP Mailer

  Created by: shunsuk - http://d.hatena.ne.jp/shunsuk/
  Version: 0.6
  Contact: http://twitter.com/shunsuk/

This extension extends Mailer Extension to send Japanese mails.


== Requirements

Mailer Extension: http://ext.radiantcms.org/extensions/127-mailer


== Installation

1. Install Mailer Extension:

http://ext.radiantcms.org/extensions/127-mailer

2. Get the latest version of JP Mailer Extension code:

  cd vendor/extensions

    git clone git://github.com/shusnuk/jp_mailer.git jp_mailer

3. Modifie environment.rb

  config.extensions = [ :mailer, :jp_mailer, :all ]


